summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing construction of Contract No. 7 of the West Seattle-Alki Sewer Improvement Project for the construction of storm drains to separate existing combined sewers in the Gatewood District of West Seattle generally bounded by Southwest Hudson Street and Southwest Raymond Street on the north, 34th Avenue Southwest on the east, Southwest Frontenac Street and Southwest Myrtle Street on the south and 41st Avenue Southwest and Beach Drive Southwest on the west, and making an appropriation from the Sewer Improvement Fund therefor.
